{"tid":1222521,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"田北俊發表聲明 呼籲自由黨支持擱置修例刻不容緩","createTime":"2019-06-14T12:43:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T13:02:05.000Z","uid":5195,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b05d58d3c38a82a0ab348cf91fd74c1a66a72db3","tid":1222521,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T12:43:25.000Z","msg":"繼實政圓桌議員田北辰公開呼籲政府暫緩修訂《逃犯條例》，其兄長、自由黨榮譽主席田北俊發表聲明，「關於修訂逃犯條例為香港帶來的連場衝突，我再次呼籲黨內各位議員支持擱置修例，刻不容緩。」<br />\n<br />\n田北俊在聲明中指出，「我們一起經歷很多風雨，你們也是有良知的好友。我相信你們可以在這艱難的時刻，為香港市民打下一支強心針，令大家在這遍我們熱愛的土地上繼續樂業安居。」"},{"pid":"b25c0258a414ca7c1e65287883b10fbe1487d171","tid":1222521,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T12:57:58.000Z","msg":"田少：我美國d資產呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b71a5e430bb7d64ab96c480d29cb44aab0660650","tid":1222521,"uid":7763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T12:59:11.000Z","msg":"會唔會太遲<br />\n凍完資產<br />\n票都唔撚投比你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a956d46b4d81816fbad792940479bae648c41be","tid":1222521,"uid":40267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b25c0258a414ca7c1e65287883b10fbe1487d171","tid":1222521,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T12:57:58.000Z","msg":"田少：我美國d資產呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T13:02:05.000Z","msg":"今次唔關大少事掛"}]}